@startuml
top to bottom direction
skinparam componentStyle rectangle
skinparam linetype ortho

title Customer Support Automation - System Architecture (Logical View)

actor Customer
actor "Support Agent" as Agent
actor "Support Manager" as Manager

component "SMTP Gateway" as SMTP
component "Application Services\n- Listener\n- Triage\n- Orchestration\n- Ticket Sync\n- Communication\n- Admin API" as Services
component "Monday.com Adapter" as MondayAdapter
component "Claude Adapter" as ClaudeAdapter

component "Redis Queue/Cache" as Redis
database "MongoDB" as Mongo
component "Secret Manager" as Secrets
component "Observability\n(Logs, Metrics, Traces)" as Obs

Customer -down-> SMTP : support request
SMTP -down-> Services : inbound/outbound mail
Services -down-> ClaudeAdapter : triage calls
Services -down-> MondayAdapter : ticket sync calls
Services -down-> Redis : async events
Services -down-> Mongo : state and audit data
Services -down-> Secrets : credentials
Services -down-> Obs : telemetry

Services -down-> Agent : escalation and review tasks
Agent -down-> Services : approve/override
Manager -down-> Services : SLA and reports
SMTP -down-> Customer : acknowledgement/updates

@enduml
